NB Alts Pre-MBA Analyst Hire: A growing team within NB Alts is looking for someone with 1-2 years of work experience for a first year Analyst Position.

Responsibilities
Monitoring and helping to maintain Client Relationship Management System (CRM) – Salesforce Database;
Tracking current and historical key metrics of Portfolio Companies; summarizing them into useful formats, presentations and charts;
Heavy Excel and PowerPoint presentation work: preparing pitch-books, marketing decks, business plans, spreadsheets and databases;
Monitoring and cataloging industry research
Creating and maintaining a comprehensive service provider index for internal use;
Collecting and analyzing data statistics from our portfolio companies, summarizing them into useful formats, presentations and charts;
Aggregating organizational data and providing high level analytics;
Work on analytics and graphics for industry thought leadership whitepapers;
Work on client newsletters
Supporting other team members with projects

Requirements
At a minimum, an undergraduate degree with excellent academic credentials 1-2 years of experience at a top tier investment bank, asset management firm or management consultant;
Self-starting attitude, entrepreneurial spirit, strong judgment and real-time critical thinking skills;
Highly organized with the ability to multi-task—a fine-tuned attention to detail;
Superior ability to synthesize and communicate complex information into a presentable format using PowerPoint;
Strong analytical skills with advanced experience using Excel;
Strong understanding of and intellectual curiosity about the hedge fund and private equity industries;
Ability to articulate and present ideas effectively both orally and in written form;
Team-player attitude and a desire to work on a wide range of projects
